{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":119,"text":"[This talk contains graphic content.\nViewer discretion is advised.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":4278,"text":"This is Nina Rodríguez's Facebook profile."},{"time":9072,"text":"This person had three different profiles"},{"time":11286,"text":"and 890 kids between 8 and 13 years old\namong her friends list."},{"time":18827,"text":"These are excerpts of a chat\nwith one of those kids."},{"time":25385,"text":"This is an exact copy of the chat."},{"time":28650,"text":"It's part of the case file."},{"time":32886,"text":"This kid started sending private photos"},{"time":36366,"text":"until his family realized\nwhat was going on."},{"time":39871,"text":"The police report and subsequent\ninvestigation lead them to a house."},{"time":45409,"text":"This was the girl's bedroom."},{"time":50451,"text":"Nina Rodríguez was actually\na 24-year-old man"},{"time":55482,"text":"that used to do this with lots of kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61471,"text":"Micaela Ortega was 12 years old"},{"time":64697,"text":"when she went to meet\nher new Facebook friend,"},{"time":67496,"text":"also 12."},{"time":69667,"text":"\"Rochi de River,\" was her name."},{"time":74142,"text":"She actually met Jonathan Luna,\nwho was 26 years old."},{"time":78611,"text":"When they finally caught him,"},{"time":80285,"text":"he confessed that he killed the girl\nbecause she refused to have sex with him."},{"time":86696,"text":"He had four Facebook profiles"},{"time":89706,"text":"and 1,700 women on his contact list;"},{"time":95003,"text":"90 percent of them\nwere under 13 years old."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100529,"text":"These are two different\ncases of \"grooming\":"},{"time":104195,"text":"an adult contacts a kid\nthrough the internet,"},{"time":108263,"text":"and through manipulation or lying,\nleads that kid into sexual territory --"},{"time":112631,"text":"from talking about sex"},{"time":114526,"text":"to sharing private photos,"},{"time":116734,"text":"recording the kid using a webcam"},{"time":118975,"text":"or arranging an in-person meeting."},{"time":122527,"text":"This is grooming."},{"time":124589,"text":"This is happening, and it's on the rise."},{"time":129727,"text":"The question is: What are we going to do?"},{"time":132207,"text":"Because, in the meantime, kids are alone."},{"time":136724,"text":"They finish dinner, go to their rooms,"},{"time":138764,"text":"close the door,"},{"time":140964,"text":"get on their computer, their cell phones,"},{"time":143411,"text":"and get into a bar,"},{"time":146704,"text":"into a club."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150284,"text":"Think for one second\nabout what I've just said:"},{"time":154752,"text":"they're in a place full of strangers"},{"time":157624,"text":"in an uninhibited environment."},{"time":161853,"text":"The internet broke physical boundaries."},{"time":164744,"text":"When we're alone in our bedroom\nand we go online,"},{"time":168799,"text":"we're not really alone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173460,"text":"There are at least two reasons\nwhy we're not taking care of this,"},{"time":178164,"text":"or at least not in the right way."},{"time":181779,"text":"First, we're sure that everything\nthat happens online is \"virtual.\""},{"time":186210,"text":"In fact, we call it \"the virtual world.\""},{"time":191019,"text":"If you look it up in the dictionary,"},{"time":193816,"text":"something virtual is something\nthat seems to exist"},{"time":196315,"text":"but is not real."},{"time":199028,"text":"And we use that word\nto talk about the internet:"},{"time":203224,"text":"something not real."},{"time":206867,"text":"And that's the problem with grooming."},{"time":209274,"text":"It is real."},{"time":211714,"text":"Degenerate, perverted adults\nuse the internet to abuse boys and girls"},{"time":217552,"text":"and take advantage of, among other things,"},{"time":219661,"text":"the fact that the kids and their parents\nthink that what happens online"},{"time":223095,"text":"doesn't actually happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227631,"text":"Several years ago,\nsome colleagues and I founded an NGO"},{"time":231364,"text":"called \"Argentina Cibersegura,\""},{"time":233332,"text":"dedicated to raising awareness\nabout online safety."},{"time":238678,"text":"In 2013, we attended meetings\nat the House of Legislature"},{"time":242903,"text":"to discuss a law about grooming."},{"time":247688,"text":"I remember that a lot of people thought"},{"time":249987,"text":"that grooming was strictly a precursor"},{"time":252183,"text":"to arranging an in-person meeting\nwith a kid to have sex with them."},{"time":258247,"text":"But they didn't think about what happened\nto the kids who were exposed"},{"time":261875,"text":"by talking about sex\nwith an adult without knowing it,"},{"time":265904,"text":"or who shared intimate photos thinking\nonly another kid would see them,"},{"time":269674,"text":"or even worse,"},{"time":271887,"text":"who had exposed themselves\nusing their web cam."},{"time":274875,"text":"Nobody considered that rape."},{"time":279227,"text":"I'm sure lots of you find it odd to think\none person can abuse another"},{"time":283568,"text":"without physical contact."},{"time":285742,"text":"We're programmed to think that way."},{"time":289183,"text":"I know, because I used to think that way."},{"time":291274,"text":"I was just an IT security guy"},{"time":295348,"text":"until this happened to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299423,"text":"At the end of 2011,"},{"time":302179,"text":"in a little town in Buenos Aires Province,"},{"time":304742,"text":"I heard about a case for the first time."},{"time":308780,"text":"After giving a talk,"},{"time":311288,"text":"I met the parents of an 11-year-old girl\nwho had been a victim of grooming."},{"time":318114,"text":"A man had manipulated her\ninto masturbating in front of her web cam,"},{"time":322161,"text":"and recorded it."},{"time":324207,"text":"And the video was on several websites."},{"time":328981,"text":"That day, her parents asked us, in tears,"},{"time":331686,"text":"to tell them the magic formula"},{"time":333252,"text":"for how to delete those videos\nfrom the internet."},{"time":338036,"text":"It broke my heart and changed me forever"},{"time":341717,"text":"to be their last disappointment,\ntelling them it was too late:"},{"time":345671,"text":"once content is online,"},{"time":348241,"text":"we've already lost control."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352714,"text":"Since that day, I think about that girl"},{"time":357110,"text":"waking up in the morning,\nhaving breakfast with her family,"},{"time":360676,"text":"who had seen the video,"},{"time":363211,"text":"and then walking to school, meeting\npeople that had seen her naked,"},{"time":368664,"text":"arriving to school, playing with\nher friends, who had also seen her."},{"time":374830,"text":"That was her life."},{"time":377502,"text":"Exposed."},{"time":381761,"text":"Of course, nobody raped her body."},{"time":385355,"text":"But hadn't her sexuality been abused?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":390723,"text":"We clearly use different standards\nto measure physical and digital things."},{"time":397363,"text":"And we get angry at social networks"},{"time":399323,"text":"because being angry with ourselves\nis more painful and more true."},{"time":404775,"text":"And this brings us\nto the second reason why"},{"time":406837,"text":"we aren't paying proper\nattention to this issue."},{"time":410180,"text":"We're convinced that kids\ndon't need our help,"},{"time":414693,"text":"that they \"know everything\"\nabout technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420092,"text":"When I was a kid,"},{"time":422590,"text":"at one point, my parents started\nletting me walk to school alone."},{"time":427329,"text":"After years of taking me by the hand\nand walking me to school,"},{"time":432476,"text":"one day they sat me down,"},{"time":434086,"text":"gave me the house keys"},{"time":435953,"text":"and said, \"Be very careful with these;\ndon't give them to anyone,"},{"time":439964,"text":"take the route we showed you,\nbe at home at the time we said,"},{"time":444143,"text":"cross at the corner,\nand look both ways before you cross,"},{"time":446906,"text":"and no matter what,\ndon't talk to strangers.\""},{"time":452967,"text":"I knew everything about walking,"},{"time":455888,"text":"and yet, there was a responsible adult\nthere taking care of me."},{"time":460886,"text":"Knowing how to do something is one thing,"},{"time":462886,"text":"knowing how to take care\nof yourself is another."},{"time":466649,"text":"Imagine this situation:"},{"time":468561,"text":"I'm 10 or 11 years old,\nI wake up in the morning,"},{"time":471149,"text":"my parents toss me the keys and say,"},{"time":473289,"text":"\"Seba, now you can walk to school alone.\""},{"time":476487,"text":"And when I come back late,"},{"time":479535,"text":"they say, \"No, you need to be home\nat the time we said.\""},{"time":484826,"text":"And two weeks later,"},{"time":486714,"text":"when it comes up,\nthey say, \"You know what?"},{"time":489847,"text":"You have to cross at the corner,\nand look both ways before crossing.\""},{"time":494815,"text":"And two years later, they say,"},{"time":497481,"text":"\"And also, don't talk to strangers.\""},{"time":502866,"text":"It sounds absurd, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":506312,"text":"We have the same absurd behavior\nin relation to technology."},{"time":510129,"text":"We give kids total access"},{"time":512296,"text":"and we see if one day, sooner or later,"},{"time":515160,"text":"they learn how to take care of themselves."},{"time":518942,"text":"Knowing how to do something is one thing,"},{"time":520970,"text":"knowing how to take care\nof yourself is another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524703,"text":"Along those same lines,\nwhen we talk to parents,"},{"time":527304,"text":"they often say they don't care\nabout technology and social networks."},{"time":534202,"text":"I always rejoin that by asking\nif they care about their kids."},{"time":537976,"text":"As adults, being interested\nor not in technology"},{"time":540464,"text":"is the same as being interested\nor not in our kids."},{"time":543310,"text":"The internet is part of their lives."},{"time":546700,"text":"Technology forces us to rethink\nthe relationship between adults and kids."},{"time":552984,"text":"Education was always based\non two main concepts:"},{"time":556208,"text":"experience and knowledge."},{"time":560687,"text":"How do we teach our kids to be safe online\nwhen we don't have either?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":568055,"text":"Nowadays, we adults\nhave to guide our children"},{"time":570818,"text":"through what is often for us\nunfamiliar territory --"},{"time":573300,"text":"territory much more inviting for them."},{"time":577501,"text":"It's impossible to find an answer"},{"time":580593,"text":"without doing new things --\nthings that make us uncomfortable,"},{"time":583665,"text":"things we're not used to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":587581,"text":"A lot of you may think it's easy for me,"},{"time":590296,"text":"because I'm relatively young."},{"time":592681,"text":"And it used to be that way."},{"time":595342,"text":"Used to."},{"time":598249,"text":"Until last year,"},{"time":600139,"text":"when I felt the weight\nof my age on my shoulders"},{"time":605422,"text":"the first time I opened Snapchat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610390,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":614510,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":619585,"text":"I didn't understand a thing!"},{"time":623321,"text":"I found it unnecessary,"},{"time":625673,"text":"useless, hard to understand;"},{"time":628839,"text":"it looked like a camera!"},{"time":630751,"text":"It didn't have menu options!"},{"time":634760,"text":"It was the first time I felt the gap"},{"time":637472,"text":"that sometimes exists\nbetween kids and adults."},{"time":641742,"text":"But it was also an opportunity\nto do the right thing,"},{"time":645026,"text":"to leave my comfort zone, to force myself."},{"time":648948,"text":"I never thought I'd ever use Snapchat,"},{"time":652283,"text":"but then I asked my teenage cousin\nto show me how to use it."},{"time":658349,"text":"I also asked why she used it."},{"time":660788,"text":"What was fun about it?"},{"time":663738,"text":"We had a really nice talk."},{"time":665929,"text":"She showed me her Snapchat,\nshe told me things,"},{"time":668406,"text":"we got closer, we laughed."},{"time":672949,"text":"Today, I use it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674675,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":676788,"text":"I don't know if I do it right,"},{"time":678437,"text":"but the most important thing\nis that I know it and I understand it."},{"time":684406,"text":"The key was to overcome the initial shock"},{"time":688567,"text":"and do something new."},{"time":691940,"text":"Something new."},{"time":693444,"text":"Today, we have the chance\nto create new conversations."},{"time":697312,"text":"What's the last app you downloaded?"},{"time":699652,"text":"Which social network do you use\nto contact your friends?"},{"time":703074,"text":"What kind of information do you share?"},{"time":706559,"text":"Have you ever been\napproached by strangers?"},{"time":710862,"text":"Could we have these conversations\nbetween kids and adults?"},{"time":715536,"text":"We have to force ourselves\nto do it. All of us."},{"time":718243,"text":"Today, lots of kids are listening to us."},{"time":724707,"text":"Sometimes when we go\nto schools to give our talks,"},{"time":727464,"text":"or through social networks,"},{"time":729138,"text":"kids ask or tell us things"},{"time":731492,"text":"they haven't told\ntheir parents or their teachers."},{"time":735813,"text":"They tell us -- they don't even know us."},{"time":740966,"text":"Those kids need to know"},{"time":744135,"text":"what the risks of being online are,"},{"time":748174,"text":"how to take care of themselves,"},{"time":749704,"text":"but also that, fundamentally,\nas with almost everything else,"},{"time":753295,"text":"kids can learn this from any adult."}]},{"cues":[{"time":759558,"text":"Online safety needs to be\na conversation topic"},{"time":763468,"text":"in every house and every\nclassroom in the country."},{"time":767863,"text":"We did a survey this year that showed\nthat 15 percent of schools said"},{"time":772152,"text":"they knew of cases of grooming\nin their school."},{"time":775386,"text":"And this number is growing."},{"time":779830,"text":"Technology changed\nevery aspect of our life,"},{"time":783315,"text":"including the risks we face"},{"time":786080,"text":"and how we take care of ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":788506,"text":"Grooming shows us this\nin the most painful way:"},{"time":793088,"text":"by involving our kids."},{"time":796787,"text":"Are we going to do something\nto avoid this?"},{"time":800202,"text":"The solution starts\nwith something as easy as:"},{"time":804419,"text":"talking about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805708,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":806890,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}